title: East Coast College Tour 2025 | Y Combinator
content:
YC is going on a college tour! We're visiting Harvard, Yale, MIT, Columbia, Cornell, and Cornell Tech.
If you're a current student at any of those schools and interested in startups, we'd love to meet you.
Here are dates and links to sign up - please note these events are only for current students at these schools:
Cornell - Mar 23, 2025 Sign up link
Cornell Tech - Mar 25, 2025 Sign up link
Columbia - Mar 26, 2025 Sign up link
Yale - Mar 27, 2025 Sign up link
Harvard - Mar 28, 2025 Sign up link
MIT - Apr 18, 2025 Sign up link
